##### CalorieCount #####
A Toptal test project by Lara Tais


## Stack ##
django
ajax_auth
django-rest-framework
jquery


## Run ##
sudo ./deploy.sh
will activate the virtual env, install the requirements, load test users to db, collect static files and fire the django dev server


## Access ##
http://127.0.0.1:8000/


## Users ##
usernames: 'admin', 'manager', 'common_user'
all passwords are 'toptal123'


